ore":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T16:23:29.000Z","msg":"我都唔想因爲感情咁辛苦<br />\n但活著真係好痛苦<br />\n不斷思考要點做<br />\n但最後發現<br />\n自己根本冇資格去做d咩<br />\n連關心 都冇身份"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T17:29:59.000Z","msg":"我都有咁諗過<br />\n最後豁了出去搵番佢<br />\n加油啦你"},{"pid":"81198c423427109ad21b089cfcdc61ef1f798743","tid":2168314,"uid":328123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"208d80ad24068fe838b4da829e9575d68d4ce505","tid":2168314,"uid":357234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T16:31:38.000Z","msg":"搵個目標 增值下自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n飲可樂都會開心啲架"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T17:31:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 正啊可樂"},{"pid":"452b278ecf773d939e5ef6a0b3369c06b2ac7251","tid":2168314,"uid":328123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"10c5c977726b2d91b2f1e78f172c8ca4f242af2a","tid":2168314,"uid":349439,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T16:44:00.000Z","msg":"其實唔洗逼自己唔諗，越逼只會越提醒自己佢嘅存在<br />\n不如搵時間發洩乾淨自己嘅情緒，爆喊好聽歌好<br />\n然後去做唔同嘅嘢充實自己<br />\n短時間內放唔低係正常的，只要等到你痛夠心淡嘅時候自然就放到手"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T17:32:50.000Z","msg":"啱啊"},{"pid":"3e48cd9e4ee662dc0b75988c807ba91f0a2f1ad0","tid":2168314,"uid":179837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4c082b3655282b68be8aaaf330347b89944a9407","tid":2168314,"uid":361287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"38a42b371716fb9f9bc8274b6b8d5877546c8235","tid":2168314,"uid":159842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b73efa1b269447e6a19a7fd5ae5ac61812f30997","tid":2168314,"uid":361287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T17:14:22.000Z","msg":"唔理佢點解要同我分啦 都唔係重點啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T17:16:55.000Z","msg":"有無咁癡情<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T17:18:50.000Z","msg":"重點真係佢再絕情 我都放唔低<br />\n<br />\n有時真係寧願佢係出軌 可能我會